ELLA AND ALEX PIKE
10.12.1918 10.7.99-3.7.14 25.3.2000
LOVED EACH OTHER, LOVED LIFE, LOVED PEOPLE, LOVED PORTOBELLO
LOVED AND REMEMBERED EVERY DAY
DONATED BY MARGARET & DAVID"Ķ
